  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2954938/" class="title-link">人类最为大的创业史——读《长征》有感！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2954938"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/33636497/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u33636497-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/33636497/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">狼奔</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-25 15:39:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2954938_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  夜以继日的去啃，终于把一本67万字的长征读完了。期间心情五味杂陈。虽然那些英雄们史诗般的故事值得我不断的深思和悼念，但是今天我想从一个76年后的后人的角度去看看当时的情景，去分析一下当时中国工农红军长征胜利的原因。         读《长征》时我是同时看着电视剧《解放》...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2954938/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2954938_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2954938_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










